  m_Name: DoctorJournal_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 48
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD b\xE1c s\u0129 #5 \u2014 Tr\u1ED1n l\xEAn helipad"
  category: 0
  content: "T\xF4i \u0111\xE3 leo l\xEAn helipad tr\xEAn t\u1EA7ng th\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n. T\u1EEB \u0111\xE2y t\xF4i nh\xECn xu\u1ED1ng th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1
    \u2014 kh\xF3i v\xE0 l\u1EEDa kh\u1EAFp n\u01A1i. \u0110\xE1m zombie l\xF9ng
    s\u1EE5c d\u01B0\u1EDBi s\xE2n b\u1EC7nh vi\u1EC7n, ch\xFAng kh\xF4ng leo c\u1EA7u
    thang \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c n\xEAn t\u1EA1m th\u1EDDi an to\xE0n. T\xF4i mang theo
    2 l\u1ECD thu\u1ED1c gi\u1EA3i th\u1EED nghi\u1EC7m \u2014 li\u1EC1u cu\u1ED1i
    c\xF9ng. N\u1EBFu c\xF3 tr\u1EF1c th\u0103ng \u0111\u1EBFn c\u1EE9u, t\xF4i s\u1EBD
    mang theo. N\u1EBFu kh\xF4ng... t\xF4i s\u1EBD \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i 2 l\u1ECD
    n\xE0y \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y, ph\xF2ng khi c\xF3 ai t\xECm th\u1EA5y. Thu\u1ED1c
    gi\u1EA3i c\xF3 th\u1EC3 \u0111\u1EA3o ng\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xE1c d\u1EE5ng XC-1
    n\u1EBFu d\xF9ng trong 24 gi\u1EDD \u0111\u1EA7u sau khi b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn. Sau
    24 gi\u1EDD th\xEC v\xF4 d\u1EE5ng. B\xE1c s\u0129 Edward."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
